[
  {
    "text": "I know we've all lost stuff...",
    "start": 5.22,
    "duration": 1.84
  },
  {
    "text": "and you think life takes more than it gives...",
    "start": 7.06,
    "duration": 2.8
  },
  {
    "text": "but not today.",
    "start": 9.96,
    "duration": 1.46
  },
  {
    "text": "Today it's giving us something.",
    "start": 11.42,
    "duration": 1.66
  },
  {
    "text": "It's giving us a chance.",
    "start": 13.48,
    "duration": 1.64
  },
  {
    "text": "To do what?",
    "start": 15.32,
    "duration": 1.26
  },
  {
    "text": "To give a crap.",
    "start": 16.79,
    "duration": 1.32
  },
  {
    "text": "Very well.",
    "start": 19.467,
    "duration": 0.84
  },
  {
    "text": "huh?",
    "start": 22.254,
    "duration": 0.5
  },
  {
    "text": "Wait. What are you doing man?",
    "start": 22.88,
    "duration": 1.36
  },
  {
    "text": "You said to give a crap!",
    "start": 24.46,
    "duration": 1.52
  },
  {
    "text": "NO NO! That is not what I meant at all!",
    "start": 25.98,
    "duration": 2.36
  },
  {
    "text": "I am groot!",
    "start": 28.34,
    "duration": 1.5
  },
  {
    "text": "How Guardians of the Galaxy Should Have Ended",
    "start": 30.54,
    "duration": 2.0
  },
  {
    "text": "Bring me the orb!",
    "start": 36.78,
    "duration": 1.67
  },
  {
    "text": "Why exactly?",
    "start": 38.45,
    "duration": 1.56
  },
  {
    "text": "What?!",
    "start": 40.073,
    "duration": 0.5
  },
  {
    "text": "I mean all you do is sit in that chair ALL DAY LONG!",
    "start": 40.6,
    "duration": 3.74
  },
  {
    "text": "Is NOT having the orb going to change anything about your daily routine?",
    "start": 44.54,
    "duration": 4.1
  },
  {
    "text": "I will rule the universe, AND sit in this chair.",
    "start": 48.8,
    "duration": 3.23
  },
  {
    "text": "So bring me the orb, boy!",
    "start": 52.24,
    "duration": 2.24
  },
  {
    "text": "Why don't you get up out of that chair and make me?",
    "start": 54.64,
    "duration": 1.74
  },
  {
    "text": "I can't get out of this chair...",
    "start": 56.38,
    "duration": 1.826
  },
  {
    "text": "it's not my time...",
    "start": 58.68,
    "duration": 1.9
  },
  {
    "text": "plus",
    "start": 60.854,
    "duration": 0.5
  },
  {
    "text": "my legs are asleep.",
    "start": 61.54,
    "duration": 1.48
  },
  {
    "text": "You're so weird, Thanos!",
    "start": 63.02,
    "duration": 2.02
  },
  {
    "text": "Infinity waaaaar! Mwahahaha!",
    "start": 65.26,
    "duration": 3.78
  },
  {
    "text": "We have to get out of here!",
    "start": 71.14,
    "duration": 1.04
  },
  {
    "text": "I hope you have a plan!",
    "start": 72.19,
    "duration": 1.34
  },
  {
    "text": "I have a plan!",
    "start": 73.68,
    "duration": 0.88
  },
  {
    "text": "Do not shoot those windows one at a time!",
    "start": 74.56,
    "duration": 1.974
  },
  {
    "text": "All of you fire at the same window on my command!",
    "start": 76.733,
    "duration": 3.12
  },
  {
    "text": "Ready?!",
    "start": 80.26,
    "duration": 0.76
  },
  {
    "text": "Oh man!",
    "start": 81.28,
    "duration": 1.1
  },
  {
    "text": "Fire!",
    "start": 82.48,
    "duration": 0.64
  },
  {
    "text": "How would you like to get paid?",
    "start": 87.4,
    "duration": 1.84
  },
  {
    "text": "How do you think, man? Units.",
    "start": 89.42,
    "duration": 1.66
  },
  {
    "text": "Very well.",
    "start": 91.18,
    "duration": 0.82
  },
  {
    "text": "Carina, dont!",
    "start": 93.113,
    "duration": 0.96
  },
  {
    "text": "I will no longer be your slave!",
    "start": 94.09,
    "duration": 2.82
  },
  {
    "text": "*zap*",
    "start": 97.04,
    "duration": 0.66
  },
  {
    "text": "Oh dude!",
    "start": 98.273,
    "duration": 0.56
  },
  {
    "text": "Sorry! That girl look like she was about to get in between me and becoming stupid rich...",
    "start": 100.1,
    "duration": 5.04
  },
  {
    "text": "he he he. That'll be four billion units please.",
    "start": 105.14,
    "duration": 3.5
  },
  {
    "text": "*whistles*",
    "start": 111.015,
    "duration": 3.88
  },
  {
    "text": "Yes!",
    "start": 125.348,
    "duration": 0.5
  },
  {
    "text": "Your salvation is at hand!",
    "start": 128.318,
    "duration": 3.391
  },
  {
    "text": "Raaaaaah!",
    "start": 131.709,
    "duration": 1.411
  },
  {
    "text": "*sings* Ooo child, it's about to get easy times.",
    "start": 133.12,
    "duration": 3.7
  },
  {
    "text": "Ooo child, things'll be bright now.",
    "start": 137.0,
    "duration": 2.74
  },
  {
    "text": "What are you doing?",
    "start": 139.92,
    "duration": 1.74
  },
  {
    "text": "Dance off, bro! Me and you.",
    "start": 141.738,
    "duration": 1.76
  },
  {
    "text": "Some day! Something something in the beautiful sun!",
    "start": 144.24,
    "duration": 4.16
  },
  {
    "text": "Oh. Whatever. It's your funeral.",
    "start": 148.4,
    "duration": 2.033
  },
  {
    "text": "*smash*",
    "start": 150.433,
    "duration": 1.36
  },
  {
    "text": "And then, I totally destroyed EVERYTHING.",
    "start": 154.04,
    "duration": 2.78
  },
  {
    "text": "*laughter*",
    "start": 156.96,
    "duration": 2.88
  },
  {
    "text": "That's my jam!",
    "start": 160.04,
    "duration": 1.22
  },
  {
    "text": "Take my hand!",
    "start": 163.74,
    "duration": 1.78
  },
  {
    "text": "Dude! Let go!",
    "start": 174.04,
    "duration": 1.52
  },
  {
    "text": "No way!",
    "start": 175.72,
    "duration": 0.76
  },
  {
    "text": "What do we do now!?",
    "start": 178.069,
    "duration": 1.14
  },
  {
    "text": "I don't know!",
    "start": 179.253,
    "duration": 0.88
  },
  {
    "text": "What you want to do? Something good?",
    "start": 186.099,
    "duration": 2.151
  },
  {
    "text": "Something bad?",
    "start": 188.25,
    "duration": 1.5
  },
  {
    "text": "Little bit of both?",
    "start": 189.75,
    "duration": 1.197
  },
  {
    "text": "We'll follow your lead, Star-Lord.",
    "start": 191.56,
    "duration": 2.82
  },
  {
    "text": "Wait. So who's the good and who's the bad?",
    "start": 197.843,
    "duration": 2.72
  },
  {
    "text": "Hey. I'm batman. You wanna know my secret identity?",
    "start": 200.7,
    "duration": 4.3
  },
  {
    "text": "Do you want a fist to the face?",
    "start": 205.02,
    "duration": 1.9
  },
  {
    "text": "Nevermind. He's the bad.",
    "start": 206.92,
    "duration": 1.654
  },
  {
    "text": "Me?! If anything I'm the good, and you're the bad.",
    "start": 208.753,
    "duration": 3.28
  },
  {
    "text": "Or WE'RE the good and THEY'RE the bad.",
    "start": 212.033,
    "duration": 1.994
  },
  {
    "text": "Or You're the BAD and we're the GOOD, and Bla Bla Bla!",
    "start": 214.027,
    "duration": 3.346
  },
  {
    "text": "This conversation bores my brain!",
    "start": 217.373,
    "duration": 1.811
  },
  {
    "text": "So, welcome back to earth I suppose.",
    "start": 219.532,
    "duration": 2.4
  },
  {
    "text": "This is awesome! There are so many things I've missed out on!",
    "start": 221.932,
    "duration": 2.748
  },
  {
    "text": "I got this new thing called, iPod...",
    "start": 224.796,
    "duration": 2.4
  },
  {
    "text": "There's like a bazillion songs on it!",
    "start": 227.196,
    "duration": 2.082
  },
  {
    "text": "♬ butt you got a butt I got a but we all have butts. ♬",
    "start": 229.278,
    "duration": 2.898
  },
  {
    "text": "You guys sing a lot about butts now!",
    "start": 232.194,
    "duration": 2.32
  },
  {
    "text": "Why do you do that?",
    "start": 234.621,
    "duration": 1.2
  },
  {
    "text": "I don't know.",
    "start": 236.014,
    "duration": 0.88
  },
  {
    "text": "Music got weird.",
    "start": 236.98,
    "duration": 1.2
  },
  {
    "text": "So anyways. You guys saved the galaxy!",
    "start": 238.18,
    "duration": 2.453
  },
  {
    "text": "A lot of pilots died, but hey you all held hands at the end and sort of made it all better.",
    "start": 240.633,
    "duration": 3.92
  },
  {
    "text": "Yeah no kidding.",
    "start": 244.6,
    "duration": 1.26
  },
  {
    "text": "You also left an infinity stone in a city that barely has any protection left.",
    "start": 245.86,
    "duration": 3.436
  },
  {
    "text": "Did you see where I got the stone the first time?",
    "start": 249.296,
    "duration": 2.258
  },
  {
    "text": "There was like nobody guarding it.",
    "start": 251.56,
    "duration": 1.64
  },
  {
    "text": "You guys and your infinity stones.",
    "start": 253.2,
    "duration": 1.882
  },
  {
    "text": "So you're like half human and half something else...",
    "start": 255.082,
    "duration": 3.124
  },
  {
    "text": "Are you not the least bit interested in knowing who your own dad is?",
    "start": 258.206,
    "duration": 2.715
  },
  {
    "text": "What? Sorry I didn't hear you!",
    "start": 261.072,
    "duration": 2.001
  },
  {
    "text": "Did you know they made transformers movies!?",
    "start": 263.073,
    "duration": 2.64
  },
  {
    "text": "They look so weird!",
    "start": 265.86,
    "duration": 1.56
  },
  {
    "text": "He asked who your father is!",
    "start": 267.54,
    "duration": 2.52
  },
  {
    "text": "They made Ninja Turtles into a movie too! Several times!",
    "start": 270.22,
    "duration": 3.88
  },
  {
    "text": "I feel like he's conveniently dodging this topic.",
    "start": 274.1,
    "duration": 2.233
  },
  {
    "text": "You! One who is part bat and part man...",
    "start": 276.48,
    "duration": 2.8
  },
  {
    "text": "Who is your father?",
    "start": 279.356,
    "duration": 1.28
  },
  {
    "text": "Oh I'm not part bat. I just dress like a bat...",
    "start": 280.636,
    "duration": 2.952
  },
  {
    "text": "Because I'm b...",
    "start": 283.588,
    "duration": 1.026
  },
  {
    "text": "Why do you dress like a bat?",
    "start": 284.614,
    "duration": 1.26
  },
  {
    "text": "To strike fear in the hearts of my enemies. Duh.",
    "start": 285.874,
    "duration": 3.12
  },
  {
    "text": "Bats are not scary. Bats are tiny mammals.",
    "start": 288.994,
    "duration": 2.62
  },
  {
    "text": "Bats are totally scary!",
    "start": 291.614,
    "duration": 1.292
  },
  {
    "text": "You should be called \"Normal Man who dresses As Bat\".",
    "start": 293.58,
    "duration": 3.06
  },
  {
    "text": "I'm not just a normal man...",
    "start": 296.64,
    "duration": 1.767
  },
  {
    "text": "I'm Batman!",
    "start": 298.58,
    "duration": 0.98
  },
